@Override public TokenStream create(TokenStream tokenStream) {     return new ASCIIFoldingFilter(tokenStream, false). }

@Override public TokenFilterFactory getSynonymFilter() {     if (preserveOriginal == false) {         return this.     } else {         // See https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-7536 for the reasoning         return new TokenFilterFactory() {              @Override             public String name() {                 return ASCIIFoldingTokenFilterFactory.this.name().             }              @Override             public TokenStream create(TokenStream tokenStream) {                 return new ASCIIFoldingFilter(tokenStream, false).             }         }.     } }

public TokenStream normalize(TokenStream tokenStream) {     // Normalization should only emit a single token, so always turn off preserveOriginal     return new ASCIIFoldingFilter(tokenStream, false). }
